Instructions and Specifications of how to compile, 
install and execute the PSO implementation and configure the robot swarm controller:

- the language used is Python3 so just install python3 

- to run the PSO : 
    - first manually set the random seeds in the 10 different decision-making{i}.argos where i is between 1 and 10
    
    - then, run "python3 pso.py" in terminal
    
- The results are shown in terminal and the csv + boxplots files are created in the "Results" file



